Notice that the equations $x - z = 0,$ $x - 2y + z = 0,$ and $x + y + z = 0$ represent three planes that intersect at the origin, and this forms a three-dimensional figure with faces that are equilateral triangles, each with side length $\sqrt{36} = 6.$

